{"word":"βραβεύω","slug":"βραβεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βραβεύω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βραβεύς'><el>βραβεύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to act as a judge</i> or <i>umpire</i>, <b><a href='S:Isocrates'>Isocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to arbitrate, decide on</i>, <el>τὰ δίκαια</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:— <i>to direct, arrange, control</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}